import React from 'react'
import { Card } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Gallery = () => {
  return (
    <Card className='my-3 rounded'>
      <Row className='my-3'>
        <Col md={3}>
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c1.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c2.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c17.jpg'} variant='top' />
        </Col>

        <Col md={3}>
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c4.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c5.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c6.jpg'} variant='top' />
        </Col>

        <Col md={3}>
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c7.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c8.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c9.jpg'} variant='top' />
        </Col>

        <Col md={3}>
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c13.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c15.jpg'} variant='top' />
          <Card.Img src={'/Cake/c12.jpg'} variant='top' />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Gallery
